E(X)=p\cdot 0 + (1-p)(n+1)=1
p=\frac{n}{n+1}
\sum_{i=0}^n X_i \leq n \Rightarrow X_i\leq n , \forall i=1..n\Rightarrow X_i=0, \forall i=1..n
X_i=0, \forall i=1..n \Rightarrow\sum_{i=0}^n X_i=0 \leq n
\sum_{i=0}^n X_i \leq n \iff X_i=0, \forall i=1..n
P\left(\sum_{i=0}^n X_i \leq n\right)=P(X_i=0, \forall i=1..n)=p^n=\left(\frac{n}{n+1}\right)^n
